cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.COM. 

The paper deals with pilot allocation in massive MIMO systems for M2M communication, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), control and systems engineering (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). The focus on M2M communication and the use of massive MIMO systems suggest that cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories. The mention of collision resolution protocols and access success probability analysis also point towards cs.SY and cs.COM. Finally, the use of simulations and performance evaluation suggest cs.MM as a possible category.
